    "Section 2: Deep Learning's Rise in HealthcareA game-changing technology in the healthcare industry is deep learning.",
    "The analysis of medical images, the diagnosis of diseases, the creation of new drugs, and other fields have advanced significantly as a result of deep neural networks' ability to automatically learn and extract features from complex data.",
    "Deep learning has completely changed how different diagnostic modalities, such radiology, pathology, and ophthalmology, are interpreted in the realm of medical imaging.",
    "A subset of deep learning models called convolutional neural networks (CNNs) have demonstrated extraordinary performance in image categorization tasks.",
    "The examination of retinal pictures serves as the major diagnostic tool for diabetic retinopathy, making CNNs an obvious candidate for automation."
